description.narrative: UNICEF supported the national response to the emergency generated by hurricanes Eta/Iota, through an intervention that integrated the different components of the CCCs, and focused especially on the most excluded population groups of the North Caribbean Coast.WASH and Nutrition, Protection, and Health and Education activities were complemented and reinforced by communication campaigns and the promotion of positive habits, which also considered the COVID-19 pandemic. A robust monitoring system was developed for all these activities | Status:On-track | As-of Date:23/01/2022
